-----
Asset

Available Commands:
  create-gateway    create a gateway
  edit-gateway      edit a gateway
  issue-asset       issue an asset
  query-asset       Query details of a asset
  query-gateway     Query details of a gateway of the given moniker
  query-gateways    Query all gateways with an optional owner
  query-gateway-fee Query the creation fee for a gateway with the given moniker



1. native
    1）自己issue
       gas高
       Denom = [Family].[Source].[ID]

    2）注意点：
        2.1 owner不可以当operator
        2.2 当Source为gateway时，Asset的Owner和Operators为空
        2.3 issue的时候只能用iris
        2.4 "Total Supply" can be changed via "Mint" or "Burn" operations
            "Owner" can be transfered via "Owner Transfer" operation (Native tokens only)
            "Operators" can be updated via "Operator Edit" operation (Native tokens only)
        2.5 创建网关/发行(Issue)资产/增发(Mint)资产，除了正常的交易手续费，还需额外支付一笔固定的资产费用（见下面的参数说明）

2. external （proposal）
    1）external tokens没有owner
    Pre-config

3. gateway （网关）
    1）gateway tokens属于gateway


operators：
除了转移owner 其他权限都有。  2/3以上同意可以转移owner

